{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-201-to-300/problem-285-pythagorean-odds","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"project-euler-problems-201-to-300","demoType":null,"title":"Izazov 285: Pitagorejeva mogućnost","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Albert bira pozitivan ceo broj $k$, zatim dva realna broja $a$, $b$ slučajno se biraju u intervalu [0,1] sa normalnom distribucijom.</p>\n<p>Koren iz zbira kvadrata ${(ka + 1)}^2 + {(kb + 1)}^2$ se izračunava, a zatim zaokružuje do najbližeg celog broja. Ako je rezultat jednak $k$, dobija bod $k$; inače ne dobija nijedan bod.</p>\n<p>Na primer, ako $k = 6$, $a = 0.2$ i $b = 0.85$, onda ${(ka + 1)}^2 + {(kb + 1)}^2 = 42.05$. Kvadratni koren 42.05 je 6.484... i zaokruženo do najbližeg celog broja, postaje 6. Ovo je jednako $k$, pa dobija ocenu 6.</p>\n<p>Može se pokazati da ako igra 10 kola i $k = 1, k = 2, \\ldots, k = 10$, očekivana vrednost njegovog ukupnog rezultata, zaokružena na pet decimala, je 10.20914.</p>\n<p>Ako igra runde ${10}^5$ i za $k = 1, k = 2, k = 3, \\ldots, k = {10}^5$, koja je očekivana vrednost njegovog ukupnog rezultata, zaokružena na pet decimala?</p>\n</section>","id":"5900f48a1000cf542c50ff9c","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"","notes":null,"challengeType":1,"helpCategory":"Euler","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"project-euler","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":301936,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-201-to-300/problem-285-pythagorean-odds"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"scriptjs","ext":"js","name":"script","contents":"function pythagoreanOdds() {\n\n  return true;\n}\n\npythagoreanOdds();","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["script.js"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p><code>pythagoreanOdds()</code> trebalo bi da vrati <code>157055.80999</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(pythagoreanOdds(), 157055.80999);"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/project-euler/#project-euler-problems-201-to-300","dashedName":"problem-285-pythagorean-odds","certification":"project-euler","disableLoopProtectTests":true,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"project-euler","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"project-euler-problems-201-to-300","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-201-to-300/problem-286-scoring-probabilities","prevChallengePath":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-201-to-300/problem-284-steady-squares","id":"5900f48a1000cf542c50ff9c","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":1,"challengeFiles":[{"name":"script","ext":"js","contents":"// solution required","history":["script.js"],"fileKey":"scriptjs"}]}},"id":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-201-to-300/problem-285-pythagorean-odds"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3858520367"],"slicesMap":{}}